<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821900>
    dc:description "FIGURES 950–954. Stephanodes septentrionalis Huber, gaster except 952. 950a, dorsal; 950b, ovipositor seen through gaster; 951, lateral; 952, male head, anterior; 953, genitalia seen through gaster; 954, male, lateral. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821900/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821902>
    dc:description "FIGURES 955–960. Stephanodes sp., head, male except for 958. 955, anterior; 956, posterior; 957, lateral; 958, dorsal; 959, ventral; 960, mouthparts. Scale bars=50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821902/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821896>
    dc:description "FIGURES 943–946. Stephanodes septentrionalis Huber, head except 946. 943, anterior; 944, posterior; 945a, lateral; 945b, lateral (internal) showing ocular apodeme; 946, antenna. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821896/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821904>
    dc:description "FIGURES 961–969. Stephanodes sp., mesosoma, except 967–969. 961, dorsal; 962, lateral; 963, ventral; 964, ventral with coxae; 965, anterior; 966, scutellum–propodeum; 967, petiole, dorsal; 968, petiole, lateral; 969, petiole, ventral. Scale bars: 961–966=100 μm; 967–969=50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821904/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821894>
    dc:description "FIGURE 942. Stephanodes septentrionalis Huber, habitus. Canada, Quebec, James Bay hwy, km 221, 10.vi.1985, H. Goulet. Scale bar=1000 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821894/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821898>
    dc:description "FIGURES 947–949. Stephanodes septentrionalis Huber. 947, mesosoma, dorsal; 948, mesosoma, lateral; 949, wings. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821906>
    dc:description "FIGURES 970–973. Stephanodes sp., metasoma. 970, male, dorsal; 971, lateral; 972, male, anterior; 973, ventral. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

